snippet.title: Marvel Animation's Marvel Zombies - Official Teaser Trailer #2 (2025) Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd
snippet.description:
Don't miss the Teaser Trailer #2 for Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies, an animated horror installment to the Marvel Cinematic Universe distributed by Marvel Studios. This series re-contextualizes the Marvel Universe as Earth's mightiest heroes go head-to-head against a zombie outbreak, turning even the strongest of them into undead nightmares. Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

After the Avengers are overtaken by a zombie plague, a desperate group of survivors discover the key to bringing an end to the super-powered undead, racing across a dystopian landscape and risking life and limb to save their world. 
 
Marvel Zombies stars Elizabeth Olsen, Paul Rudd, Florence Pugh, David Harbour, Tessa Thompson, Simu Liu, Awkwafina, Hailee Steinfeld, Wyatt Russell, Randall Park, Iman Vellani, Dominique Thorne, and more. The series is executive produced by Kevin Feige, Louis D’Esposito, Brad Winderbaum, Dana Vasquez-Eberhardt, Bryan Andrews, and Zeb Wells, and is produced by Danielle Costa, Carrie Wassenaar. 

Marvel Animation’s Marvel Zombies will be a four-part event on September 24, streaming exclusively on Disney+.

#IGN #Marvel #MCU

snippet.title: Heartland, Season 19 | Official Trailer!
snippet.description:
In Season 19 the Bartlett-Fleming family must risk everything to keep Heartland and those they love out of harm’s way. Amy strikes a delicate balance between her commitment to a new relationship and always putting her daughter first. However, when her reputation as a horse trainer is called into question, she’s caught off guard and Amy must fight to save her good name.

Lou tries to refocus her attention on her family – and not on work, but when a new adversary threatens the ranch, Lou is forced to make some difficult choices. Jack is the steadfast rancher he’s always been, but his patience is tested after he hires an unlikely new ranch hand. And when outside forces jeopardize Heartland, Amy, Jack, Lou and the rest of the family must come together to build an even stronger foundation for the future. Each holding fast to their values in the face of it all. Heartland strong.

It is the land where people stand together in every storm, ready to live, love, and even die for each other. Punjab is fire, Punjab is faith, Punjab is love — a place where passion runs deeper than rivers, and where humanity knows no religion. snippet.title: Critical Role IV | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The wolves are at Thjazi Fang's door...but the real story is just beginning.
Check out our official trailer of Campaign 4! 

Tune in for the premiere of Campaign 4 on Thursday, October 2nd at 7pm PT on Beacon, YouTube, and Twitch.

New Episodes Release Weekly on Thursdays.

Learn more about Campaign 4 at https://critrole.com/campaign4/ 

SHOW DESCRIPTION
Hero to many. Enemy to some. When Thjazi Fang is marked for execution, various figures from across his remarkable life unite to uncover the truth behind his grim fate. In a land still suffering from the fallout of dead gods and living in the shadow of a tumultuous rebellion, these disparate people will come together across the fractured world of Aramán and connect in ways they never imagined. 
As hope and victory fade, a question hangs over Aramán. Without the Gods, what great deeds now fall to us? And who, or what, shall grab their crown for themselves?

snippet.title: XLG vs. SEN — VALORANT Champions Paris — Group Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world’s top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We’re proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:

snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution | Official Trailer - In Theatres December 5
snippet.description:
JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution
From MAPPA
Based on the Shonen Jump manga by Gege Akutami

The best of the Shibuya Incident arc combines with the debut of the first two episodes of Season 3's Culling Game arc in this exclusive theatrical event!

Coming to North America exclusively in movie theatres starting December 5.
Follow @GKIDSFilms for more updates!
https://brnw.ch/21wVRcH

A veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.

Yuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.

In the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.

The desperate confrontation between Satoru Gojo’s two beloved students comes to the big screen with an early preview. Be the first to experience Yuji and Yuta’s fateful battle with the hotly anticipated kickoff to Season 3 in theatres nationwide.

snippet.title: The Last Frontier — Official Trailer | Apple TV+
snippet.description:
A lone U.S. marshal leads the hunt for escaped convicts in the Alaskan wilderness. Starring Jason Clarke, Dominic Cooper, Haley Bennett, Simone Kessell, and Alfre Woodard. The Last Frontier premieres October 10 on Apple TV+ https://apple.co/_TheLastFrontier_

The Last Frontier follows Frank Remnick (Clarke), the lone U.S. marshal in charge of the quiet, rugged barrens of Alaska. Remnick’s jurisdiction is turned upside-down when a prison transport plane crashes in the remote wilderness, setting free dozens of violent inmates. Tasked with protecting the town he’s vowed to keep safe, he begins to suspect the crash wasn’t an accident, but the first step of a well-crafted plan with far-reaching and devastating implications.

In addition to Clarke, the ensemble cast includes Dominic Cooper (“The Gold”), Haley Bennett (“The Magnificent Seven”), Simone Kessell (“Yellowjackets”), Dallas Goldtooth (“Reservation Dogs”), and Tait Blum (“For All Mankind”), with Academy Award Nominee and multi-Emmy winner Alfre Woodard (“Clemency”).

Hailing from Apple Studios, The Last Frontier is executive produced by Bokenkamp and D’Ovidio, who also serve as writers, alongside Clarke, Laura Benson (“The Big C”), Glenn Kessler (“Bloodlines”), Albert Kim (“Nikita”), and series episodic director Sam Hargrave (“Extraction”).

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukkoyen po
Un mela kaadhal vachene
Thothadhaalum theerala
Ponadhaalum maarala 

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukko di po
Ennalum Kaadhal kuthadhu 
Parvayal Yenga Vechaale 

Paakaama pesaama seraama ponaalum 
Ennaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum
Neeyaachum nallaaru po
 
Kaadhalaa en nenjam
Yekkamaa aanan naane
Kaayamaa nee senjum
Sirikkirene
Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po
